ComicInfo.Title: Galactus Found!
ComicInfo.Summary: Galactus Found!: Thor takes the Odinship in search of Galactus. Galactus captures the Odinship and begins to tell his origin to Thor. Meanwhile, on Earth, a foreign country completes their creation of the Thermal Man and rockets him to the US to wreak havoc.
